[I] MCP server for databases

[T] MCP Toolbox for Databases is an open source MCP server for databases. It
[T] enables you to develop tools easier, faster, and more securely by handling
[T] the complexities such as connection pooling, authentication, and more.

[U] https://github.com/googleapis/genai-toolbox

[A] Google APIs
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/ai
[F] CROSS

[L] APL
[V] 0.31.0

[D] 361459aeca3c9f1492e9ae2c4acd8bc60abe04afbb153cd2d617cc9d genai-toolbox-0.31.0.tar.gz https://github.com/googleapis/genai-toolbox/archive/v0.31.0/

. $base/package/*/*/go-conf.in
hook_add postmake 5 'cp -vf genai-toolbox $root$bindir/toolbox'
